    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, trim then chop your<strong> green beans</strong> in half</p><p>Chop your<strong> tomato[es]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
