    {
      "instruction": "<p>Fluff the <strong>cooked rice</strong> with a fork</p><p>Add your <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>and mix until fully combined – this is your<strong> seasoned rice</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>seasoned rice</strong> to the pan and give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> plant-based chickpea & green bean curried rice</strong></p>",
